and photograph them.

39:00.621 --> 39:02.612
I try to approach people with respect,

39:02.690 --> 39:05.716
I try not to speak too loud,
or move too fast.

39:07.895 --> 39:09.453
I want to be open.

39:10.965 --> 39:13.456
I want to feel open
in my heart towards them.

39:14.068 --> 39:17.196
And... they do sense it.

39:18.973 --> 39:20.668
